transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hello, Charles. My name is James Inyart. I was wanting to refill my prescription.

Speaker 2: Okay. Can I have your phone number, please, James?

Speaker 1: It's 417-818-3160.

Speaker 2: Okay. And we need a refill on the 100-milligram generic Vitagra 12-count?

Speaker 1: Yeah. Sildenafil 100-milligram.

Speaker 2: Okay. Perfect. Are we still shipping to 10712 West Farm Road, 178 Republic, Missouri? 6573?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: All right. Let's do it. I still have a MasterCard ending in 5855. That expires on 06 of 28.

Speaker 1: Is that still a good card to process on?

Speaker 2: Yes. Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay. Going to refill now. Standard free shipping, right?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay. Perfect. All right, James. Everything went through. I'd assume everything to arrive by maybe Thursday or Friday of next week, okay?

Speaker 2: Okay. Hey, what's the total on that?

Speaker 1: $103.95.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Will you guys send me – will you send me a receipt?

Speaker 1: Yeah, 100%.

Speaker 2: W-E-S-E-N-Y-A-R-T at Gmail?

Speaker 1: Yep.

Speaker 2: All right. Sounds good. We'll send an email once everything gets processed, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay. Thanks a lot.

Speaker 2: Absolutely. Hope you have a good one.

Speaker 1: You too. Bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
